## What is LIT?

The Leaders in Training program is designed for students ages 15–17 to experience an incredible adventure of following Christ and developing their leadership skills alongside a real summer camp session.

Through first-hand experience and hands-on learning, you will focus on your God-given strengths while deepening your faith, growing in community, and becoming a servant-hearted leader who is mission-minded.

{% ctaButton
