## Servant Leadership

Camp Otyokwah's LIT program is a volunteer, servant leadership experience for high school students. This program has become a critical part of the summer — benefiting the staff, the campers, and the entire camp community.

LIT is intentionally designed to teach leadership skills, positive and responsible work habits, teamwork, and to encourage excellence in all we do for the Lord (Col 3:23).

